What's the error message in log file LastTest.log? Search "AttentionPastState_dynamic" in the log file, and if the error is like
```
The difference between f_expected[i] and f_output[i] is 0.001, which exceeds 0.0005
```
As long as the difference is small (< 0.005), I think it is fine. We can change the threshold to avoid such error.
Short term you can also skip the tests with the `--skip_tests` build parameter if that particular operator isn't relevant to you or the difference in the output is in fact small.
